der text-muted-foreground/80 font-outfit">Topo da trilha</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-xl font-extrabold text-foreground font-outfit">R$ 1M</h3><p class="mt-1.5 text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground font-openSauce font-normal">A placa que marca um novo nível de faturamento e vira símbolo real da marca que você criou.</p></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="faq" class="relative overflow-hidden pb-24 pt-8"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="mb-12 text-center reveal-up "><h2 class="text-balance text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-salt md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-outfit">Perguntas <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-sharp via-sky-sharp to-light-blue-sharp bg-clip-text text-transparent font-extrabold">Frequentes</span></h2><p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-pretty text-lg text-[#F9F9F9]/70 font-openSauce font-light">Tudo o que você precisa saber sobre a Sharpify</p></div><div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[640px] flex-col gap-3"><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">Como funciona a entrega automática?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Assim que o pagamento (Pix ou Cartão) é aprovado, o sistema envia o produto digital instantaneamente para o cliente via e-mail ou Discord, sem que você precise intervir.</p></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">Quais são as taxas da Sharpify?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Temos as menores taxas do mercado. No plano gratuito, a taxa é de apenas 1% por venda no site e 0% pelo Discord, permitindo que você lucre muito mais a cada transação.</p></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">Preciso saber programar para criar minha loja?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Não! Oferecemos templates prontos e totalmente customizáveis. Você pode editar cores, fontes e layout através do nosso painel intuitivo sem precisar entender de programação.</p></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">Como recebo os pagamentos das minhas vendas?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Os pagamentos caem na sua carteira interna da Sharpify. Você pode acompanhar seu saldo em tempo real e solicitar o saque para sua conta bancária de forma simples e direta.</p></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">O bot do Discord está incluso em todos os planos?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Sim! Todos os planos permitem conectar o bot no seu servidor para receber notificações de vendas em tempo real e realizar a entrega automática de produtos via DM.</p></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-blue-sharp/10 bg-ocean-sharp/15 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-sharp/35 hover:bg-ocean-sharp/30 cursor-pointer"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-5 px-5 py-[18px]"><span class="flex-1 text-salt text-base font-semibold font-outfit leading-6">Posso usar meu próprio domínio na loja?</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-sky-sharp transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div><div class="overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0"><p class="px-5 text-sm leading-6 text-[#F9F9F9]/80 font-openSauce font-light transition-all duration-300 pb-0 pt-0">Sim! Você pode conectar um domínio personalizado (como minhaloja.com.br) para passar ainda mais credibilidade aos seus clientes, sem custos ocultos.</p></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class="relative border-t border-border/50 bg-background/80"><div class="section-divider"></div><div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12"><div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg